  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nIn prater, when any validators join sync committee period, the performance is very bad. This maybe related to #3416 where we subscribe to all sync committee subnets with `subscribeAllSubnets` flag\r\n\r\nOn Nov 17, some validators joined the sync committee\r\n<img width=\"1580\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-11-19 at 10 06 08\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/142558181-323cf971-0752-455c-b090-24cf9ff56cd8.png\">\r\n\r\nMore FINDNODES dscv5 query were issues, more dial rate\r\n<img width=\"1620\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-11-19 at 10 09 18\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/142558452-2d3333a0-b297-48ae-910e-e12303bfcb3b.png\">\r\n\r\nAt the same time, there are a lot of Goodbye sent/received, a lot of ping/metadata/status request/response too\r\n<img width=\"1621\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-11-19 at 10 10 25\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/142558579-6b0d38a1-f9f2-4f1c-bc6d-07eed286c0f9.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\nGossip block is delayed a lot\r\n<img width=\"1586\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-11-19 at 10 07 07\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/142558260-13022f7a-9105-4fd1-90ea-3d800060dc41.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nNo performance issue\r\n\r\n",
